            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_91gc' title='Col. 91GC &mdash; HL Deb 25 January 1996 vol 568 c91GC' name='column_91gc' href='#column_91gc' rel='bookmark'>91GC</a>
            theatre. Perhaps he can write to me and tell me how the rank structure and discipline will work in theatre for sponsored reservists once they are called up.</p><p>
            Clause 38 agreed to.</p><p>
